title: 7 AM HOUR - Mom, Why Is Your Butt So Big?
description: It's Falen and Jenny today so bear with us while Jenny tries to run equipment with only one good hand, lol!  Falen tells a story about how Olive embarrassed her the other day and then we have other parents call in with their stories of how their child embarrassed them, Mixtape Game, find out what "Sugar Mama Weekend" is all about, and more!
